    </p>


    \[
    \left 
    \lbrace 
    \begin{aligned} 
    v_0\cos\alpha &= v\cos\beta, \\ 
    v_0\sin{\alpha}-gT &= -v\sin\beta \\
    \end{aligned}
    \right.
    \]

